data.description: Easy to show! Assumable FHA mortgage at 5.49%. Huge chefs kitchen with an island, bar, granite countertops and stainless appliances including the refrigerator and a breakfast area. This home has luxury vinyl plank flooring thru-out and carpet in the bedrooms.  There is a mantle with a cool shiplap electric fireplace in the living room and a barn door leading into the laundry room.  Amazing open floorplan. All bedrooms are separate Also has a separate dining room which could easily be used a office, den or even a 5th bedroom. Primary suite is spacious and has a double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, walk-in closet and an enclosed water closet. Private back yard is privacy fenced with a newly added covered patio and an above ground pool perfect for cooling off on those hot summer days.  Large corner lot located on a cul-de-sac just a few lots next to the community stocked pond. Gold fortified roof good thru March 2028 (see docs).
